title: Ballots arrive at Germany's SPD for coalition count
text:
Ballots arrive at Germany's SPD for coalition count   00:59 
Germany's Social Democrats prepared to count the votes of hundreds of thousands of party members who will decide the fate of a new coalition under Chancellor Angela Merkel. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
